    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for the intro. Could you expand on that a bit more? Maybe add some specific examples of cases or legal arguments that show how it's been used to push back against unfair laws. I want the students to really understand how it functions as a shield for these rights.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
